Definition at line 163 of file propvar.h.

#define DEFINE_CBufferAllocator__Allocate
 

Value:

VOID *                                                          \
CBufferAllocator::Allocate(ULONG cb)                            \
{                                                               \
    VOID *pv;                                                   \
                                                                \
    cb = (cb + sizeof(LONGLONG) - 1) & ~(sizeof(LONGLONG) - 1); \
    if (cb > _cbFree)                                           \
    {                                                           \
        return(NULL);                                           \
    }                                                           \
    pv = _pvCur;                                                \
    _pvCur = (BYTE *) _pvCur + cb;                              \
    _cbFree -= cb;                                              \
    return(pv);                                                 \
}
